author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a game known as "Paradise" that bolsters a very similar look to GTA Online. This game on close inspection actually appears to steal not only assets but entrap people into a shady dealing of cryptocurrency where they'll lose not just their time but also their money. It should be shut down. Thanks for watching!

title: Massive GTA 6 Scam Situation...
